SeizureWarningText: IMPORTANT HEALTH WARNING: READ BEFORE PLAYING A very small percentage of individuals may experience epileptic seizures when exposed to certain light patterns or flashing lights, including some of the visual effects that appear in certain video games. Symptoms may even be experienced by individuals with no history of epilepsy or photosensitivity. If you or anyone in your family have an epileptic or photosensitivity condition, please consult your physician before playing. If you experience any of the following symptoms while playing this video game, immediately discontinue use and consult your physician before resuming play: dizziness, altered vision, eye or muscle twitches, loss of awareness, disorientation, any involuntary movement, or convulsions.

Description/landingleg_2v_anchored: As its name implies, the LT-09 landing leg is designed to hold and anchor itself into almost any surface, making it a great choice for landing vehicles on uneven terrain. Our engineers brag it is so powerful yet precise that it can grab onto the surface of Minmus without excessive cracking.
